  "text": "Self, in a paper published in 1990, claimed that ITSs should be viewed as an engineering design field. Therefore, ITS design should be guided by methods and techniques appropriate for design [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Twenty years after Self's claim, ITSs had become a growing field with signs of vitality and self-confidence [CITATION_3] .",
